# 🚗 Car Rental System (Java)

## 📌 About

Simple Java project created to practice **interfaces** and **Object-Oriented Programming (OOP)** concepts.

The system calculates the rental price based on time and applies tax using an interface.

---

## 🧠 Concepts Used

- Interfaces  
- OOP  
- Encapsulation  
- Date/Time with `LocalDateTime`  

